   : belowVAL and sellersAggressive ? "SELLERS IN CONTROL BELOW VAL\nDISTRIBUTION ZONE ACTIVE"
   : "NO CLEAR INEFFICIENCY\nWAIT FOR REJECTION OR BREAK"

